    • Method Detail

      • createFormat

        OWLDocumentFormat createFormat()
        Create a new format. Note that ontology formats currently carry prefix information for the ontology, so an instance cannot, in general, be reused for multiple parsings.
        Returns:
        new storer

      • getKey

        String getKey()
        Returns the key for the OWLOntologyFormat that this class is a factory for without necessarily creating an instance of the OWLOntologyFormat.
        Returns:
        The key for the OWLOntologyFormat.

      • isTextual

        boolean isTextual()
        Returns true if this format can be represented using textual characters. Returns false if this format must be dealt with using binary methods.
        Returns:
        True if this format is textual, and false if it is a binary format.
